{"tid":953423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【本土研究社】檔案解密漸見曙光","createTime":"2018-12-24T02:37:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T05:44:39.000Z","uid":138409,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e4eb9e6e4ac0fc78e83735f778f93a8bb32b5dc6","tid":953423,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T02:37:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kimching.geographer/posts/10156104492106247\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkimching.geographer%2Fposts%2F10156104492106247&d=shPZLtxq8zKrM9oTtNKLMaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=3fe2bab1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kimching.geographer/posts/10156104492106247</a><br />\n多謝各位早期對我地個 香港前途研究計劃 Decoding Hong Kong's History 既支持，上次籌足給5位研究員約5萬到英國國家檔案館的基本行程開支，我地解密檔案工作既成果開始顯現了。<br />\n<br />\n早前聽過有啲關注同做檔案研究既前輩指導建議，我地一直追縱緊80年代近6成 (有過千份) 過左期都未解封同香港有關既英國機密檔案。可知道本身機密檔案要封30年係因為佢機密，30年再封30年個啲夠期唔解封既檔案，意思係機密中既機密，好多都係以外交關係為由唔開放。<br />\n<br />\n於是，我地年初試下就呢堆有關政制、基本法、城市土地、社會民生等不同主題既「超級機密檔案」，利用英國《資訊自由法》進行上訴，要求以公眾利益理由提早公開。<br />\n<br />\n經過漫長同國家檔案館既書信往來，今月試左10份有4份局部開放，有1份全面開放，開放密檔既成功率比想像中高，報導一出，開始引起到大家對資訊自由法立法的關注，亦開始聽到有不同團體都希望一起參與系統性上訴的解密工作，對檔案研究同香港歷史甚有裨益。<br />\n<br />\n所以我地既檔案研究計劃除左分析檔案，建立檔案庫，同時間都兼顧著爭取解封更多檔案的工作，都係靠好多熱心既研究成員同義工朋友共同協力。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家認同我們的檔案工作，可以小額支持一下我地明年檔案研究計劃既基本研究開支 (約13萬)，做更多出色既檔案研究、檔案法倡議同解封行動出黎，會係對我地研究員同義工既鼓勵!<br />\n<br />\n🤓建檔偉業　繼續支持檔案研究計劃<br />\n<a href=\"https://liber-research.com/research-category/archival-research/?fbclid=IwAR1yJ_Uuc8e0GKBN23GeT6oRuMNTkAUEtCUVAQ4aZ3LkYNVk6UFFgW-OmJU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fliber-research.com%2Fresearch-category%2Farchival-research%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1yJ_Uuc8e0GKBN23GeT6oRuMNTkAUEtCUVAQ4aZ3LkYNVk6UFFgW-OmJU&d=shPZLtxq8zKrM9oTtNKLMaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=d55e5225\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://liber-research.com/research-category/archival-research/?fbclid=IwAR1yJ_Uuc8e0GKBN23GeT6oRuMNTkAUEtCUVAQ4aZ3LkYNVk6UFFgW-OmJU</a>"},{"pid":"f922e196a97fa064cb7d4afef994f6ec62831ed3","tid":953423,"uid":5298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T02:44:04.000Z","msg":"G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a19ad7eb3cd6182ba571b1c0c03c6a80627d0da4","tid":953423,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T04:03:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02162447919f07d656fa325b1668ac2a92d0ab51","tid":953423,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T05:02:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fcba38a931757d009049f6e41c2535fbea793f68","tid":953423,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T05:04:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629fc3362afb71d4882d3187a2800c65ce6be8a8","tid":953423,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T05:06:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c3cc61206307c2e36bf2230167d441c4dab62cf","tid":953423,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T05:40:21.000Z","msg":"猛料<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0321934d78723b386d1c3fb4eaddf633e4d7823","tid":953423,"uid":175577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T05:41:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"035aad924f2432b70a8eda150afc6677ec3c332c","tid":953423,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T05:44:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}